<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />按<colour id="1" /><colour id="65535" /><delay8 />就可以像在自己家一样，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />自由地更换布置！<10_4 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />另外，用来装饰场景的<delay8 />
家具和杂货等，<delay20 />是和<colour id="1" />Nook购物<colour id="65535" />
签订了租借协议的<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以只要是刊登在
<tag a="110" b="1" /><colour id="1" />目录<colour id="65535" />中的物品，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />都可以立即拿来装饰！</message>
	<message label="112_01" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那些可以<colour id="1" />改造<colour id="65535" />的家具，<delay20 />
