<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以就按自己的喜好来制作场景吧！</message>
	<message label="112_02" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />对了对了！<delay20 />说起来<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />完成<colour id="3" />Nook Inc.<colour id="65535" />的<delay8 />
